OL,3,C'Men in wigs and brown make-up taking
OL,4,Cstunt jobs from black women' ` study
OL,6,F"Men wearing wigs and using brown make-
OL,7,Fup" are depriving black women and
OL,8,Fmembers of other ethnic groups of top
OL,9,Fstunt roles in movies, according to a
OL,10,Fnew study.
OL,12,FDr Laura Crossley, a researcher at
OL,13,FBournemouth University, has found that
OL,14,Fdespite an increase in female action
OL,15,Froles in the movies, women still
OL,16,Fstruggle to get into core stunt teams
OL,18,FShe said: "It is very difficult for
OL,19,Fstunt women to become part of regular
OL,20,Fcrews.
