OL,3,C'Men in wigs and brown make-up taking
OL,4,Cstunt jobs from black women' ` study
OL,6,F"Because the industry has been male
OL,7,Fdominated so long, most stunt co-
OL,8,Fordinators on film sets are men.
OL,10,F"As a result, you can end up with male
OL,11,Fco-ordinators hiring other men and
OL,12,Fputting them in drag to perform
OL,13,Fstunts, or even using men wearing
OL,14,Fbrown make-up and wigs to double for
OL,15,Fwomen of colour."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@QO]
