OL,3,C'Men in wigs and brown make-up taking
OL,4,Cstunt jobs from black women' ` study
OL,6,FThe study, published in the Journal of
OL,7,FBritish Cinema and Television,
OL,8,Fhighlights that an increase in action
OL,9,Fheroines from different ethnic groups
OL,10,Fon screen has led to greater demand
OL,11,Ffor female stunt doubles from those
OL,12,Fbackgrounds.
OL,14,FDr Crossley said that performers like
OL,15,FMarie Mouroum and Belle Williams, who
OL,16,Fhave carried out stunts in the Bond
OL,17,Ffranchise as MI6 agent Nomi and Eve
OL,18,FMoneypenny respectively, "represent
OL,19,Fpositive steps but they are exceptions
OL,20,Frather than the rule".
