OL,3,C'Men in wigs and brown make-up taking
OL,4,Cstunt jobs from black women' ` study
OL,6,FFor the study, Dr Crossley spoke to
OL,7,Fstunt directors Annie Lees-Jones and
OL,8,FTiger Lilli Rudge.
OL,10,FShe said: "One of the things Tiger
OL,11,Fsuggested was that when a male stunt
OL,12,Fco-ordinator is appointed, the
OL,13,Fproducers should hire a woman
OL,14,Falongside him, training her so that
OL,15,Fshe gets more experience.
OL,17,F"At the moment the co-ordinators tend
OL,18,Fto hire performers who they have
OL,19,Fworked with in the past, and they are
OL,20,Fusually men.
